# 🔍 Log Analyzer (Python)

## 📌 Overview
This project analyzes authentication logs and detects suspicious failed login attempts.

## 🎯 Features
- Parses log files
- Detects failed logins
- Counts attempts per IP
- Flags suspicious activity

## 🛠️ Technologies
- Python 3
- Regex / string parsing

